id: pm-ukml
title: "GH-596: update-many --ids must report nonexistent requested IDs"
description: "Bulk explicit-ID mutations silently omit nonexistent IDs while reporting a fully successful matched subset, so agents cannot distinguish a complete request from a partial one."
type: Issue
status: in_progress
priority: 2
tags[5]: agent-ux,"area:cli",bulk-ops,data-integrity,gh-issue
created_at: "2026-07-18T15:09:38.855Z"
updated_at: "2026-07-19T12:50:17.698Z"
assignee: maintainer-agent
author: codex-root
estimated_minutes: 90
acceptance_criteria: update-many reports unmatched_ids and unmatched_count for explicit --ids; dry-run and apply envelopes agree; existing matched rows remain deterministic; CLI and contract tests cover mixed valid/missing IDs; GH-596 is resolved
parent: pm-mpbb
risk: low
confidence: high
